    "description": "The Excrypt Cryptographic Module (ECM) is a tamper-resistant / responding PCI compatible universal module that provides secure cryptographic processing. The ECM features an Ethernet 10 / 100 interface supporting up to 999 sockets, a serial port, and 1000 3DES / 1000 4096-bit RSA battery backed key storage. The ECM provides TDES and PKI support for key management and electronic payment / funds transfer security. The ECM is used in the ExcryptTM SSP, RMC, PCE, KMS, and SKI Series products.",
